room_title: Escape room "The Conari Candy Factory" by Conari Escape Rooms in Columbia (MO)
room_address: 514 E High St Jefferson City, MO 65101
room_description: The famed Conari Candy Factory is about to release a new product that will revolutionize the candy industry! This is exciting news to everyone, except you. You are the owner of a rival candy company who has been trying to get the recipe for this secret product for years! The final attempt at getting the recipe is underway. The eccentric owner of the Conari Candy Factory is giving an hour long tour to a group of kids. Use this time to sneak into his office and break into his vault to steal the recipe!
